description: Stops the directory sharing between the directory owner and consumer accounts.

parameters.name: DirectoryId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Managed Microsoft AD directory that you want to stop sharing.

parameters.name: UnshareTarget
parameters.description: Identifier for the directory consumer account with whom the directory has to be unshared. Identifier of the directory consumer account. Type of identifier to be used in the Id field.

nested_params.name: Id
nested_params.description: Identifier of the directory consumer account.

nested_params.name: Type
nested_params.description: Type of identifier to be used in the Id field.

nested_items.name: SharedDirectoryId
nested_items.description: Identifier of the directory stored in the directory consumer account that is to be unshared from the specified directory ( DirectoryId).
